'''飓风弗洛西'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Flossie}}）是2007年8月形成的一场强度虽高，但只对[[夏威夷州|夏威夷州]]构成轻微影响的[[太平洋飓风季|太平洋飓风]]，也是[[2007年太平洋飓风季|这年太平洋飓风季]]第6个获得命名的热带气旋、第2场飓风和首场大型飓风。系统源于7月21日离开非洲海岸的[[东风波|东风波]]，穿越热带大西洋后于8月1日经中美洲进入东太平洋。由于外界环境有利，系统得以发展成热带低气压，并且很快就于8月8日升级成热带风暴。

风暴总体向[[罗盘方位|西南偏西]]方向移动，虽然气象部门预计外部环境只会有小幅改善，但气旋还是在8月10日进入[[快速增强|爆发性增强期]]，于8月11日成为[[热带气旋风级|大型飓风]]，达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]220公里的最高强度。受沿途[[海面温度|海面温度]]逐渐降低、[[风切变|风切变]]也越来越多的影响，飓风稳步减弱，于8月16日降级成热带低气压。当晚，风暴中心几乎已没有强烈[[雷暴|雷暴]]活动，弗洛西因此不再属热带气旋。

面对气旋威胁，夏威夷大岛收到热带风暴警告和飓风警告。应急机构官员警告居民做好防灾措施，降雨量有可能超过300毫米，另有热带风暴强度阵风。但是，弗洛西实际产生的影响很小，夏威夷大岛的最高阵风时速约为63公里，总计降雨量不到150毫米。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Flossie 2007 track.png}}
7月21日，一股结构混乱的[[东风波|东风波]]离开非洲西海岸进入东大西洋。系统向西移动，其结构一直杂乱无章，中心附近也缺乏显著[[对流|对流]]（即降雨和[[雷暴|雷暴]]活动）。8月1日，东风波经中美洲进入东太平洋，外界环境有有大幅改善，有利于[[热带气旋|热带天气系统]]组织及强化。8月2日，系统行进至[[特万特佩克湾|特万特佩克湾]]以南附近海域，其中心不远处发展出稳固的降雨和雷暴区，但之后没有出现进一步发展。两天后，传统卫星图像显示系统内的深层对流已有增长，但其后仍然同之前一样缺乏进一步组织。8月6日，下层环流中心附近再度爆发出对流，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]预期系统即将发展成热带气旋，但系统内仍然缺少足够的降雨和雷暴来证实这一推断。8月8日，这片[[热带扰动|扰动天气]]继续西进，并且再度爆发出对流并持续了足够时间，美国画家飓风中心于是在[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]8月8日下午18点将位于[[夏威夷岛|夏威夷大岛]]东南偏东方向约2700公里洋面的系统归类为热带低气压。受高空[[反气旋|反气旋]]影响，气旋所处海域[[风切变|风切变]]很少，而且[[海面温度|海面温度]]较高，第六{{lang|en|E}}号热带低气压的组织结构继续改善，仅成形6小时后就升级成热带风暴并获名“弗洛西”（{{lang|en|Flossie}}）。<ref name="TCR">{{cite report | author = Richard J. Pasch | author2 = David P. Roberts | date = 2008-01-10 | accessdate = 2016-02-26 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | format = PDF | title = Hurricane Flossie Tropical Cyclone Report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP092007_Flossie.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002014314/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP092007_Flossie.pdf | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>

[[File:Flossie_13_aug_2007_2310Z.jpg|thumb]]

风暴位于墨西哥西南部上空[[副热带高压脊|副热带高压脊]]的西南边缘，并在其影响下总体朝[[罗盘方位|西南偏西]]方向移动，在此期间继续强化<ref>{{cite report | author = Jamie Rhome | title = Tropical Storm Flossie Discussion Number 2 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151210212058/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep09/ep092007.discus.002.shtml | date = 2007-08-08 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep09/ep092007.discus.002.shtml? | accessdate = 2016-02-26 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2015-12-10 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。8月9日，气旋各象限内的上层[[外流_(气象学)|外流]]都开始扩张，中心周围的[[雨带|螺旋带]]也变得明显<ref>{{cite report | author = Lixion A. Avila | date = 2007-08-08 | accessdate = 2016-02-26 | title = Tropical Storm Flossie Discussion Number 3 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep09/ep092007.discus.003.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002123855/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep09/ep092007.discus.003.shtml | deadurl = no }}</ref>。弗洛西的微波成像上已经可以分辨出中层[[风眼|风眼]]及其对应的风眼墙，但其传统卫星图像依然模糊不清<ref>{{cite report | author = Jamie Rhome | date = 2007-08-09 | accessdate = 2016-02-26 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002123859/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep09/ep092007.discus.006.shtml | title = Tropical Storm Flossie Discussion Number 6 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep09/ep092007.discus.006.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center }}</ref>。经过一系列卫星强度估算，同时根据可见光及红外线卫星图像上风暴的风眼进行推断，气象机构于{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}8月10日中午12点把弗洛西升级成[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下的一级飓风<ref name="TCR" />。气象部门起初预计，随着气旋朝[[夏威夷群岛|夏威夷群岛]]逼近，其外界环境会渐趋不利，但风暴实际上却得以继续增强。8月10日深夜，弗洛西出人意料地进入[[快速增强|快速增强]]期，其[[气压|气压]]迅速下降，到{{lang|en|UTC}}次日早上6点已达到[[热带气旋风级|大型飓风]]标准。这天清晨的卫星图像表明气旋的风眼约有28公里宽，周围的顶层云系温度低于-75[[摄氏度|°C]]）。<ref>{{cite report | author = Michelle Mainelli | date = 2007-08-11 | accessdate = 2016-02-26 | title = Hurricane Flossie Discussion Number 11 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep09/ep092007.discus.011.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002123927/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep09/ep092007.discus.011.shtml | deadurl = no | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref><ref>{{cite report | author = Richard J. Knabb | date = 2007-08-11 | accessdate = 2016-02-26 | title = Hurricane Flossie Discussion Number 12 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep09/ep092007.discus.012.shtml? | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002123928/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep09/ep092007.discus.012.shtml | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>11日上午，风暴跨越[[经度|西经]]140度线进入[[中太平洋飓风中心|中太平洋飓风中心]]责任区，在此期间强度又有进一步提升，于{{lang|en|UTC}}中午12点升级成四级飓风。两小时后，弗洛西达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]220公里，最低气压949[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，28.02[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高强度，是[[2007年太平洋飓风季|2007年太平洋飓风季]]最强烈的热带气旋。<ref name="TCR" />

气象部门预计弗洛西会在达到最高强度后因风切变增多而逐渐减弱，但实际情况并非如此，飓风在四级飓风强度下连续保持了36小时之久<ref name="TCR" />。中太平洋飓风中心在8月13日早间发布的公报中称，弗洛西表现顽强，没有在风切变影响下“放弃斗争”的迹象<ref name="Flossieadv20">{{cite report | author = Forecaster Houston | date = 2007-08-13 | title = Hurricane Flossie Discussion Number 20 | publisher = Central Pacific Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150128131920/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2007/TCDCP2.EP092007.20.0708131530 | url = http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2007/TCDCP2.EP092007.20.0708131530 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-02-26 | archivedate = 2015-01-28 }}</ref>。但到了8月14日凌晨，气旋开始因行经洋面水温渐低，南向风切变更趋强烈而减弱。虽然北部半圆的外流依然良好，但南半部的环流已开始消亡，南侧的风眼墙也呈现瓦解趋势。<ref>{{cite report | date = 2007-08-14 | author = Mark Powell | title = Hurricane Flossie Discussion Number 22 | publisher = Central Pacific Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-02-27 | url = http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2007/TCDCP2.EP092007.22.0708140250 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151029093909/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2007/TCDCP2.EP092007.22.0708140250 | archivedate = 2015-10-29 }}</ref>飞入系统的[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]侦察机测得每小时196公里的地面风速，还发现顶层云系在逐渐回暖，弗洛西因此降级成三级飓风<ref>{{cite report | author = Mark Powell | date = 2007-08-14 | title = Hurricane Flossie Discussion Number 24 | url = http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2007/TCDCP2.EP092007.24.0708141505 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151029110720/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2007/TCDCP2.EP092007.24.0708141505 | publisher = Central Pacific Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-02-27 | archivedate = 2015-10-29 }}</ref>。风暴还在继续减弱，侦察机经过风眼墙时测得的地面风速反而更低，气旋因此于{{lang|en|UTC}}当天中午12点从夏威夷群岛以南海域经过时进一步降级成二级飓风。8月15日，风暴残存的风眼墙被时速超过48公里的垂直风切变侵蚀<ref>{{cite report | author = Mark Powell | date = 2007-08-15 | title = Hurricane Flossie Discussion Number 26 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151029104501/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2007/TCDCP2.EP092007.26.0708150254 | url = http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2007/TCDCP2.EP092007.26.0708150254 | publisher = Central Pacific Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-02-27 | archivedate = 2015-10-29 }}</ref>，中太平洋飓风中心因此宣布弗洛西已减弱成热带风暴。{{lang|en|UTC}}8月16日早上6点，中心上空的降雨和雷暴活动已经消失，气旋降级成热带低气压。到{{lang|en|UTC}}这天中午12点时，卫星图像上仅有下层漩涡残留，弗洛西此后在夏威夷群岛西南洋面消散。<ref name="TCR" />

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:Remnants_of_Hurricane_Flossie.jpg|thumb]]
弗洛西穿越西经140度线后不久，中太平洋飓风中心向夏威夷大岛发布[[热带气旋警告|飓风观察预警]]<ref name="Flossieadv20" />。接下来几天里，飓风行进路径略比之前预测偏北，风场半径也有所扩张，中太平洋飓风中心又在之前的飓风警告基础上追加热带风暴警告<ref>{{cite report | author = Mark Powell | title = Hurricane Flossie Forecast Number 21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151029093159/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2007/TCMCP2.EP092007.21.0708132046 | publisher = Central Pacific Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-02-27 | date = 2007-08-13 | archivedate = 2015-10-29 | url = http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2007/TCMCP2.EP092007.21.0708132046 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。气象机构预计风暴可能产生暴雨并引发洪灾，因此发布[[山洪预警|山洪预警]]，政府工作人员提醒居民准备应对250至380毫米的降水。[[夏威夷州州长|夏威夷州州长]][[琳达·林格尔|琳达·林格尔]]在气旋来袭前宣布夏威夷岛进入[[紧急状态|紧急状态]]，建议当地居民储备必要物资。<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | title = Hurricane Flossie weakens as it nears Hawaii | date = 2007-08-14 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121113120511/http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/08/14/idUSN14451263._CH_.2400 | deadurl = no | publisher = Reuters | accessdate = 2016-02-27 | url = http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSN14451263._CH_.2400 | archivedate = 2012-11-13 }}</ref>

[[联邦紧急事务管理局|联邦紧急事务管理局]]向夏威夷派出20名交通、公共工程和卫生领域专家。当地开设有多个避难所，但少有居民前来躲避<ref>{{cite news | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | title = Flossie downgraded again after swiping Hawaii | date = 2007-08-15 | publisher = MSNBC | accessdate = 2016-02-27 | url = http://www.nbcnews.com/id/20228092/#.VtFg3VNnQ7I | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160124195953/http://www.nbcnews.com/id/20228092/#.VtFg3VNnQ7I | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-01-24 }}</ref>。面对风暴威胁，夏威夷州许多学府被迫关闭，其中包括[[夏威夷大学希洛分校|夏威夷大学希洛分校]]和[[夏威夷社区学院|夏威夷社区学院]]，估计有2.6万名学子只能留在家里<ref>{{cite news | title = Storm shelter, closure information | archivedate = 2013-11-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131112035732/http://www.kitv.com/weather/hurricanes/whats-closed-ahead-of-flossie/-/9327530/21216070/-/8m79wb/-/index.html | publisher = Yahoo! News | author = Brent Suyama | date = 2007-07-29 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.kitv.com/weather/hurricanes/whats-closed-ahead-of-flossie/-/9327530/21216070/-/8m79wb/-/index.html | accessdate = 2013-11-12 }}</ref>。另外还有多所图书馆、公园、私立学校、银行及商店、企业关闭。政府部门工作人员如非必要均不必上班<ref>{{cite news | author = Dan Nakaso | title = Weakened Flossie begins battering Hawaii | date = 2007-08-15 | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/storms/hurricanes/2007-08-12-flossie-hawaii_N.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130801005243/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/storms/hurricanes/2007-08-12-flossie-hawaii_N.htm | publisher = USA Today | accessdate = 2016-02-27 | archivedate = 2013-08-01 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，政府还动员应急人员做好在风暴过后快速投入救灾工作的准备<ref>{{cite news |author=Mark Niesse |title=Hurricane Flossie Storms Toward Hawaii |date=2007-08-13 |newspaper=[[华盛顿邮报|Washington Post]] |accessdate=2016-02-27 |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/08/13/AR2007081300183.html?tid=informbox |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120919071158/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/08/13/AR2007081300183.html?tid=informbox |archivedate=2012-09-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。许多游客在风暴吹袭夏威夷州前取消旅程<ref>{{cite news | author = Dan Nakaso | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121023013132/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/storms/hurricanes/2007-08-13-flossie_N.htm | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/storms/hurricanes/2007-08-13-flossie_N.htm | date = 2007-08-14 | publisher = USA Today | accessdate = 2016-02-27 | title = Skittish tourists back out before Flossie | archivedate = 2012-10-23 }}</ref>。

虽然气象机构预测夏威夷大岛东南朝向地区会出现暴雨，但由于弗洛西及时转向西进，其下层东南向风力未能在当地产生因山区地形而增强的增雨。不过，该岛北向及东北朝向区域有少量雨水，[[夏威夷县|夏威夷县]]的[[哈玛库亚|哈玛库亚]]（{{lang|en|Hamakua}}）、南希洛和[[普纳_(夏威夷州)|普纳]]（{{lang|en|Puna}}）3个区的降雨量约为25至50毫米。[[茂宜岛|茂宜岛]]的降雨量在25到76毫米之间，[[欧胡岛|欧胡岛]]的[[柯劳山脉|柯劳山脉]]有50至100毫米雨量，但风力大多不强，也没有发生严重洪灾。夏威夷岛东南海岸受到气旋产生的海浪冲击，但造成的影响很小。风暴产生的最大浪高估计有6.1米，[[卡蕾亚|南岬]]测得的持续风速至少达到每小时63公里。8月13日，岛上有一大块阶状熔岩坍塌后落入海中，有可能是因弗洛西经过引起，但也可能是由于前不久发生的5.4级地震导致。<ref>{{cite report | title = 2007 Tropical Cyclones Central North Pacific | publisher = Central Pacific Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-02-27 | url = http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/summaries/2007.php#flossie | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150907125835/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/summaries/2007.php#flossie | archivedate = 2015-09-07 | date =  }}</ref>

